## Vectron Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    C[Clients\nSDKs / Apps] -->|gRPC/HTTP| G[API Gateway]

    G -->|auth check| A[Auth Service]
    G -->|routing/meta| PD[Placement Driver]

    G -->|search cache| MC[Gateway Memory Cache]
    G -->|optional| RC[Redis/Valkey Cache]

    G -->|fanout search| W1[Worker Node 1]
    G -->|fanout search| W2[Worker Node 2]
    G -->|fanout search| WN[Worker Node N]

    W1 --> H1[HNSW Index]
    W1 --> P1[PebbleDB]
    W2 --> H2[HNSW Index]
    W2 --> P2[PebbleDB]
    WN --> HN[HNSW Index]
    WN --> PN[PebbleDB]

    G -->|optional rerank| R[Reranker]

    PD -->|Shard assignments| W1
    PD -->|Shard assignments| W2
    PD -->|Shard assignments| WN

    subgraph Workers
      W1
      W2
      WN
    end
```

## Insert/Upsert Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant PD as Placement Driver
    participant Worker as Worker Node
    participant Raft as Raft/Dragonboat
    participant Pebble as PebbleDB
    participant HNSW as HNSW Index

    Client->>APIGW: Upsert(collection, points)
    APIGW->>Auth: Validate JWT/API key
    APIGW->>PD: Resolve shard routing (cached/refresh)
    APIGW->>Worker: BatchStoreVector(shard, points)
    Worker->>Raft: Propose write
    Raft-->>Worker: Commit
    Worker->>Pebble: Persist vectors + metadata
    Worker->>HNSW: Update index (sync or async)
    Worker-->>APIGW: UpsertResponse(count)
    APIGW-->>Client: Upserted count
```

## Search Flow (Optional Vectors)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant APIGW as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant PD as Placement Driver
    participant Cache as Cache (GW/Redis)
    participant Worker as Worker Node
    participant HNSW as HNSW Index
    participant Rerank as Reranker
    participant Pebble as PebbleDB

    Client->>APIGW: Search(collection, vector, top_k, include_vectors?)
    APIGW->>Auth: Validate JWT/API key
    APIGW->>Cache: Check search cache
    alt Cache hit
        Cache-->>APIGW: Cached results
    else Cache miss
        APIGW->>PD: Get routing/shards (cached/refresh)
        APIGW->>Worker: Search shard(s) (fanout or single)
        Worker->>HNSW: ANN search
        Worker-->>APIGW: IDs + scores (+ payload)
        opt Rerank enabled
            APIGW->>Rerank: Rerank candidates
            Rerank-->>APIGW: Reranked results
        end
        APIGW->>Cache: Store results (no vectors)
    end

    opt include_vectors = true
        APIGW->>Worker: GetVector for each result (parallel)
        Worker->>Pebble: Fetch vector + metadata
        Worker-->>APIGW: Vector + metadata
    end

    APIGW-->>Client: Results (metadata + score + optional vector)
```
